Installation

1. clone the repo:
git clone https://github.com/gelgelgelo/school_labs.git


Usage

the order you proceed on these labs are:
	- control structures
	- arrays
	- functions
	- strings
	- pointers

each directory has a document that intructs you on what to 
build and how your program should behave.

once you are finised with a lab prefix the directory with "_"
example:
	arrays 		# not finished
	_arrays		# lab is completed/finised 



